{"tid":959191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"舞者參賽秀後空翻失敗　頭觸地斷頸身亡","createTime":"2018-12-28T11:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T11:42:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"37433e4eadca0d8fed09d032b0213c4fc8abd7eb","tid":959191,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"象牙海岸一名年輕舞者，參賽時表演後空翻失敗斷頸身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據《TRACE 2BABI》報導，12月21日，象牙海岸舉辦了舞蹈競賽，一名暱稱為「Internet Japonais」的年輕男舞者也前往參加，他在表演中加入後空翻的動作，第一次嘗試時失敗，之後他二度挑戰，但是這次騰空高度太低，導致他後空翻時脖子先著地，圍觀民眾發現他倒地後毫無反應，上前才看才發現他扭到脖子當場身亡。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181228/1491337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181228%2F1491337&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a2850270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181228%2F1491337&h=941572ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181228/1491337</a><br />\n<br />\n片"},{"pid":"5fd7cb700195e23a849df63612916cafdb39e3ee","tid":959191,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"淨睇標題都已經驚"}]}